targets.rawSql: SELECT count(*) FROM goals WHERE statusstorie = false and space = 'personal'
SELECT count(*) FROM goals WHERE statusstorie = false and status = 'highlight' and space = 'personal'
SELECT count(*) FROM goals WHERE statusstorie = True and space = 'personal'

select
    avg((category = 'objetivo' and statusstorie = false and space = 'personal')::int) metrics
from goals

select
    avg((category not in ('objetivos') and statusstorie = false and space = 'personal')::int) "Backlog"
from goals

select
    avg((category not in ('justified') and category in ('failed') and statusstorie = true and space = 'personal')::int) "Backlog"
from goals

select
    count(*) filter(where statusTwentyFive in ('true') and space = 'personal') as "Started",
    count(*) filter(where statusTwentyFive in ('false') and space = 'personal') as "Not Started"
from goals

select
    count(*) filter(where statusstorie = false and category not in ('objetivos') and space = 'personal')  "No Prioritized",
    count(*) filter(where statusstorie = false and category in ('objetivos') and space = 'personal') "Prioritized"
from goals

select
    count(*) filter(where startStorie <= date_trunc('month', now()) - interval '1 month' and space = 'personal')  "1 month",
    count(*) filter(where startStorie <= date_trunc('month', now()) - interval '3 month' and space = 'personal')  "3 month",
    count(*) filter(where startStorie <= date_trunc('month', now()) - interval '6 month' and space = 'personal')  "6 month"
from goals

select
    now() as Time,
    category,
    count(category) filter(where statusstorie = false and space = 'personal')  stories
from goals 
group by category
order by stories desc

select
    now() as Time,
    count(*) 
    filter(
    where statusstorie = false 
    and space = 'personal'
    and statusTwentyFive = false
    and statusFifty = false  
    and statusSeventyFive = false 
    and statusOneHundred = false
    and category not in ('metas'))  "0%",
    count(*) filter(where statusstorie = false and statusTwentyFive = true and category not in ('metas') and space = 'personal')  "25%",
    count(*) filter(where statusstorie = false and statusFifty = true and category not in ('metas') and space = 'personal') "50%",
    count(*) filter(where statusstorie = false and statusSeventyFive = true and category not in ('metas') and space = 'personal') "75%",
    count(*) filter(where statusstorie = false and statusOneHundred = true and category not in ('metas') and space = 'personal') "100%"
from goals

select
    now() as Time,
    count(*) 
    filter(
    where statusstorie = false 
    and space = 'personal'
    and statusTwentyFive = false
    and statusFifty = false  
    and statusSeventyFive = false 
    and statusOneHundred = false
    and category in ('metas'))  "0%",
    count(*) filter(where statusstorie = false and statusTwentyFive = true and category in ('metas') and space = 'personal')  "25%",
    count(*) filter(where statusstorie = false and statusFifty = true and category in ('metas') and space = 'personal') "50%",
    count(*) filter(where statusstorie = false and statusSeventyFive = true and category in ('metas') and space = 'personal') "75%",
    count(*) filter(where statusstorie = false and statusOneHundred = true and category in ('metas') and space = 'personal') "100%"
from goals

SELECT startstorie as Time, category, cast(count(*) as int) FROM goals_history 
where space = 'personal'
group by category, Time

select
    now() as Time,
    count(*) filter(where status in ('failed') and space = 'personal')  "Failed",
    count(*) filter(where status not in ('failed') and space = 'personal') "Sucess"
from goals

select
    now() as Time,
    category,
    count(*)
from exception
where space = 'personal'
group by category

select
    now() as Time,
    reason,
    count(*)
from exception
where space = 'personal'
group by reason

select
    now() as Time,
    count(*) filter(where justified = true and space = 'personal')  "Justified",
    count(*) filter(where justified = false and space = 'personal') "Not Justified"
from exception
